<br>
8 pm PST (11 EST) Thursday servers crash<br>
12 am PST Friday Karadin checks on KT to see in what order NB should plan their mobs (yay for SoS)<br>
4 pm PST Friday Karadin recieves a tell from Malystrx of VoF that King Tormax is up<br>
9pm PST (12 pm EST) Friday King Tormax is killed by FK<br>
12am PST Friday NB moves to Kael to kill KT, but he is already dead.<br>
