<br>
Now explain something even more basic.  I got ZERO tells from anyone even remotely affiliated with FK leadership before they went to kill KT (I was on all day).  I saw ZERO questions in RTA channel about &quot;Hey, KT has been up over 24 hours, we're gonna kill him under FFA, ok?&quot;.  I got ZERO tells AFTER you killed him and Jlxaac knew you guys had killed out of turn.  Why?<br>
