<br>
The reason NB doesn't find itself in this situation is because Milambus and I make damn sure to be certain we are communicate with the rest of the community on any questionable mobs we are going to kill.  If something has been up 24 hours, I check with the guild in question first before moving on it.  Why?  Because its that important to maintain the basic premise of rotations - that you don't kill out of order.<br>
<br>
